<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ثُمَّ قَالَ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ:</span> <span class="c3">{أَفَحُكْمَ الْجَاهِلِيَّة يَبْغُونَ}</span> وَهُوَ مَا خَالَفَ كِتَابَ اللَّهِ وَحكمه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سُورَة الْمَائِدَة من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٥١)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>